							assumed by <bibl><ptr target="bib:Sankaranarayanan1977_01"/></bibl> and is indeed uncertain.</note></app></listApp></div><div type="translation"><p n="1‚Äď12"> Hail! From the
					victorious residence at KńĀŠĻáŠłćńĀli, the illustrious king
					PrŐ•thivńę[Ňõrńę]mŇęla, blessed by the feet of his parents;
